headline: Cboe Global Markets and Metaurus Advisors, LLC Collaborate on New U.S. Equity Index, First of Four in Planned Dispersion Product Suite
summary: Cboe Global Markets, Inc. (Cboe: CBOE), the world's leading derivatives and securities exchange network, and Metaurus Advisors, LLC (Metaurus), an asset management company focusing on financial innovation, today announced their collaboration on the Cboe U.S. Large-Mid Cap 100 Index (CEQX). The CEQX Index, which launched on December 20, 2024, is the first of four indices jointly developed by Cboe and Metaurus.
